WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.770 --> 00:00:09.770
- The first is you have to
start using the tools, right?

2
00:00:10.080 --> 00:00:14.620
And then the second is I'm
starting to train my mind

3
00:00:15.510 --> 00:00:18.210
to use AI

4
00:00:18.210 --> 00:00:21.630
for helping me get over the hump

5
00:00:21.630 --> 00:00:26.160
in my most gnarly problems.

6
00:00:26.160 --> 00:00:27.570
So usually when you feel,

7
00:00:27.570 --> 00:00:32.310
when you feel that sense of,
"Ugh, I don't wanna do that,"

8
00:00:32.310 --> 00:00:34.327
that usually for me is a signal like,

9
00:00:34.327 --> 00:00:38.880
"Hey, hey, hey, how about some AI," right?

10
00:00:38.880 --> 00:00:42.690
Because I don't expect it
to complete the whole task,

11
00:00:42.690 --> 00:00:44.797
but I always find that when I feel like,

12
00:00:44.797 --> 00:00:46.320
"Ugh, why do I have to do that?"

13
00:00:46.320 --> 00:00:47.790
And then I think, "Hey, wait a minute,

14
00:00:47.790 --> 00:00:50.040
is there some way to make this easier,

15
00:00:50.040 --> 00:00:51.600
to make this more palatable,

16
00:00:51.600 --> 00:00:53.850
to get myself through that
initial horrible feeling

17
00:00:53.850 --> 00:00:56.340
of, like, I don't wanna do that", with AI

18
00:00:56.340 --> 00:00:58.443
and then it gets the ball rolling.